{"tid":1528994,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國班狗已經對「黑警」「黑社會」呢類字免疫左","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:27:48.000Z","uid":11727,"like":21,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7985c2c334b475e81a4c3a4c19ce334adf26f42d","tid":1528994,"uid":11727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"依家班狗聽到班示威者話佢地，佢地都當你吹水，而且呢一類嘅口號又冇阻嚇性。<br />\n不如以後大家再見到狗一齊行個納粹禮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJhVr3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJhVr3q.jpg&h=b72923ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一黎可以襯托到班黑警嘅濫權同對香港人嘅殘忍。<br />\n二黎對外會令到外國人對班黑警留低左一個更差嘅形象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gv2qPiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGv2qPiN.png&h=a43b066e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿忘721<br />\n勿忘831<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"262f9603e0c7225649572ea92fea939475e88dd4","tid":1528994,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46507ccc7f0509fcd3704b627ee98e6a90772300","tid":1528994,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"Week1已經講過 又講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5085b94683a711e31c5e98834319c917f72c3bf","tid":1528994,"uid":123765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46507ccc7f0509fcd3704b627ee98e6a90772300","tid":1528994,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"Week1已經講過 又講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:51:44.000Z",